{"tid":2189453,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"支那VTuber希薇婭9月6日會係YouTube直播","createTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T01:26:16.000Z","uid":173921,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9a9e392eb8814513ba412ce817cd7cacf193fc","tid":2189453,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKACGer/photos/a.436998099808572/1686148061560230/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKACGer%2Fphotos%2Fa.436998099808572%2F1686148061560230%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs47ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=fbab5841\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKACGer/photos/a.436998099808572/1686148061560230/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n旗下擁有多位虛擬YouTuber的Hololive，其中國分部的一期生希薇婭將於9月6日在YouTube進行首播<br />\n<br />\n希薇婭去年11月開始活動，由於該國國情因素，Hololive中國所屬的一二期生都在bilibili進行配信，文字層面上她們是「虛擬UP主」而非「虛擬YouTuber」，而希薇婭將成為首位創立YouTube頻道，配信時以說中文(普通話)為主的Hololive中國所屬「虛擬YouTuber」<br />\n<br />\n據萌娘百科資料記載，希薇婭是英語水平不錯(口語限定)的留學生，而留學的國家是美國，所以沒有所謂的「翻牆」問題<br />\n<br />\n這消息在網絡傳開來後，有一些海外網友已經摩拳擦掌聲言準備搞事，例如屆時Super Chat課金留言一些「有趣的評論」什麼的<br />\n<br />\n#不只是ACG_is_not_fxxk_政治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ax1Mbnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax1Mbnt.jpg&h=5f624afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4faafcf0026e867ff2c4d87df1d4bb38aee60e4a","tid":2189453,"uid":12421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"受眾喺牆內<br />\n<br />\n喺牆外玩係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876ad88213fc586161d07cfd5d1d9f75836a7c86","tid":2189453,"uid":353380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"donate留個天安門事件係唔係可以收台了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991b